 109:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     *** Callback registration ***
 110:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   =============================================
 111:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 112:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 113:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   The compilation define  USE_HAL_TIM_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
 114:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
 115:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 116:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 117:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   Use Function HAL_TIM_RegisterCallback() to register a callback.
 118:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   HAL_TIM_RegisterCallback() takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle,
 119:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   the Callback ID and a pointer to the user callback function.
 120:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 121:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 122:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   Use function HAL_TIM_UnRegisterCallback() to reset a callback to the default
 123:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   weak function.
 124:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   HAL_TIM_UnRegisterCallback takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle,
 125:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   and the Callback ID.
 126:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 127:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 128:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   These functions allow to register/unregister following callbacks:
 129:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) Base_MspInitCallback              : TIM Base Msp Init Callback.
 130:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) Base_MspDeInitCallback            : TIM Base Msp DeInit Callback.
 131:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) IC_MspInitCallback                : TIM IC Msp Init Callback.
 132:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) IC_MspDeInitCallback              : TIM IC Msp DeInit Callback.
 133:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) OC_MspInitCallback                : TIM OC Msp Init Callback.
 134:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) OC_MspDeInitCallback              : TIM OC Msp DeInit Callback.
 135:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) PWM_MspInitCallback               : TIM PWM Msp Init Callback.
 136:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) PWM_MspDeInitCallback             : TIM PWM Msp DeInit Callback.
 137:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) OnePulse_MspInitCallback          : TIM One Pulse Msp Init Callback.
 138:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) OnePulse_MspDeInitCallback        : TIM One Pulse Msp DeInit Callback.
 139:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) Encoder_MspInitCallback           : TIM Encoder Msp Init Callback.
 140:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) Encoder_MspDeInitCallback         : TIM Encoder Msp DeInit Callback.
 141:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) HallSensor_MspInitCallback        : TIM Hall Sensor Msp Init Callback.
 142:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) HallSensor_MspDeInitCallback      : TIM Hall Sensor Msp DeInit Callback.
 143:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) PeriodElapsedCallback             : TIM Period Elapsed Callback.
 144:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) PeriodElapsedHalfCpltCallback     : TIM Period Elapsed half complete Callback.
 145:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) TriggerCallback                   : TIM Trigger Callback.
 146:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) TriggerHalfCpltCallback           : TIM Trigger half complete Callback.
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccbKrBA6.s 			page 4


 147:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) IC_CaptureCallback                : TIM Input Capture Callback.
 148:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) IC_CaptureHalfCpltCallback        : TIM Input Capture half complete Callback.
 149:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) OC_DelayElapsedCallback           : TIM Output Compare Delay Elapsed Callback.
 150:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) PWM_PulseFinishedCallback         : TIM PWM Pulse Finished Callback.
 151:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) PWM_PulseFinishedHalfCpltCallback : TIM PWM Pulse Finished half complete Callback.
 152:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) ErrorCallback                     : TIM Error Callback.
 153:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) CommutationCallback               : TIM Commutation Callback.
 154:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) CommutationHalfCpltCallback       : TIM Commutation half complete Callback.
 155:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) BreakCallback                     : TIM Break Callback.
 156:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) Break2Callback                    : TIM Break2 Callback.
 157:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 158:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 159:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** By default, after the Init and when the state is HAL_TIM_STATE_RESET
 160:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** all interrupt callbacks are set to the corresponding weak functions:
 161:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   examples HAL_TIM_TriggerCallback(), HAL_TIM_ErrorCallback().
 162:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 163:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 164:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   Exception done for MspInit and MspDeInit functions that are reset to the legacy weak
 165:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   functionalities in the Init / DeInit only when these callbacks are null
 166:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   (not registered beforehand). If not, MspInit or MspDeInit are not null, the Init / DeInit
 167:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     keep and use the user MspInit / MspDeInit callbacks(registered beforehand)
 168:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c **** 
 169:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****   [..]
 170:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim.c ****     Callbacks can be registered / unregistered in HAL_TIM_STATE_READY state only.
